## 🎯 Kullanım Örnekleri

### Temel Kullanım
```powershell
# Hızlı test
.\Test-PWA.ps1 --fast-mode

# Detaylı test
.\Test-PWA.ps1 -Verbose -ExportJson

# Dashboard ile
.\Test-PWA.ps1 -GenerateDashboard
```

### GitHub Actions Entegrasyonu
```yaml
name: PWA Tests
on: [push, pull_request]
jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: windows-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - run: .\Test-PWA.ps1 -Verbose
```

